POE/Component/Server/SOAP version 1.06
======================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	POE					=>	0.27
	POE::Component::Server::SimpleHTTP	=>	1.10
	SOAP::Lite				=>	0.55

